					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"If the Hamedori suit never got made and he was forgotten about a year later with the appearance of “His Sexellency,” then...",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"这个世界没有Hamedori君的人偶，由于一年后‘性帝’出现，所以被大家彻底遗忘了──。",
					{"rt2"},
