					"“If this person has switched places with you, Darling, that means they should be the leader of the former NLNS.”",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					name = {"郁子"},
					"“如果是和亲爱的互相替换的话，那个人一定会变成旧NLNS的领袖。”",
